<div class="good"><a id="agood291" href="javascript:goodNew('291','http://so.gushiwen.org/shiwenv.aspx?id=804cfb54a51e',50)"><img src="/img/good.png" / alt="赞" width="14" height="14"/><span>&nbsp;50</span></a></div>
